<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c4">[العين والصاد]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">عص:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">العُصْعُص والعُصْعوص:</span> أصل الذَّنَب، والعُصُص <span class="c2">(٤٠)</span> لغةٌ فيه.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">ورجلٌ عُصْعُص:</span> قليل الخير.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">وعَصَّ الشيءُ:</span> صَلُ‍ <span class="c4">[ب]</span> <span class="c2">(٤١)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">صع:</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">الصَّعْصَعَة:</span> التحريك والتفريق،<span class="c5"> ومنه:</span> ذهبت الإِبلُ صعاصِع.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">وصَعْصَعَ رأسَه:</span> رَجَّلَه ودَهَنه.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">وتَصَعْصَعَ الرجلُ:</span> جَبُن <span class="c2">(٤٢)</span>.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">والصَّعْصَع:</span> طائر أبرش لا يقف بمكان.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">وَصَعْصَعَ الرجلُ:</span> أقبل.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">والصَّعْصَعَة:</span> نَبْتٌ يُشْرَب ماؤه للمشي.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(٤٠) في ك: والعصعص.<br>(٤١) الزيادة من ك.<br>(٤٢) «جبن» لم ترد في ك.</p> </div>